Package: rfeVIP
Type: Package
Title: Package To Perform Recursive Feature Elimination Based On Random Forest Variable Importance Parameter
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-09-28
Author: Karthik Padmanabhan
Maintainer: Karthik Padmanabhan <kpadmana@purdue.edu>
Description: This package performs recursive feature elimination based on the variable importance parameter
in random forest models using caret. The program removes negative VIPs and stops when all remaining VIPs
are positive.
License: MIT
LazyData: TRUE
